Tomato based Curry

Per Large Tomato, diced:
1/4 Onion, chopped
1tsp Cumin Seed, whole
1tsp Turmeric, ground
2tsp Smoked Paprika
1tbsp cooking oil
salt, pepper

Begin by frying spices and onion in a medium skillet. 
When onion is evenly coated and heated through, add tomato and simmer until tomato has broken down completely. 
Mixture should be thick and spreadable. 

Serve on flatbread or with rice. 
